Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请  法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好红
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为哥哥说午饭不带了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以决定在早餐上多花功夫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,花功夫…
